{"tid":481704,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後竟然用中文譯名黎講戲名，仲以為得粗人先會用！","createTime":"2017-11-27T12:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T09:07:16.000Z","uid":19334,"like":8,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74b14b9226ecc96fd637a274c0f02e05b08800ba","tid":481704,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"話說小妹說不上係真文青，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但都十分之喜愛藝術，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而新出果套Loving Vincent都十分討我歡心，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢種賞心樂事當然要分享，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁今日食Lunch果陣就分享下啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就話呢排睇左Loving Vincent，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我見隻90後眉頭一皺，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該聽唔明我講乜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪問下佢呢排睇左咩好睇既，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢答我「正義聯盟」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開頭以為係李偲嫣拍戲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾諗兩一陣先知原來係Justice League，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到有番咁上下知識水平（佢讀ivy），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都會用一向咁詞不達意嘅中文譯名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07273c713944bed74940a8891ac622e5a1c3cf06","tid":481704,"uid":80736,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/202323_4a6bbfdb8b8a51134c067c4d7b550932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-